public ExtendedStatsAggregationBuilder sigma(double sigma) {     if (sigma < 0.0) {         throw new IllegalArgumentException("[sigma] must be greater than or equal to 0. Found [" + sigma + "] in [" + name + "]").     }     this.sigma = sigma.     return this. }

@Override protected ExtendedStatsAggregatorFactory innerBuild(SearchContext context, ValuesSourceConfig<Numeric> config, AggregatorFactory<?> parent, Builder subFactoriesBuilder) throws IOException {     return new ExtendedStatsAggregatorFactory(name, config, sigma, context, parent, subFactoriesBuilder, metaData). }
